00232 static StructRNA *rna_NodeSocket_refine(PointerRNA *ptr)
00233 {
00234     bNodeSocket *sock = (bNodeSocket*)ptr->data;
00235     
00236     if (sock->default_value) {
00237         /* This returns the refined socket type with the full definition
00238          * of the default input value with type and subtype.
00239          */
00240         
00241         #define SUBTYPE(socktype, stypename, id, idname) \
00242         { \
00243             bNodeSocketValue##stypename *value = (bNodeSocketValue##stypename*)sock->default_value; \
00244             if (value->subtype == PROP_##id) \
00245                 return &RNA_NodeSocket##stypename##idname; \
00246         }
00247         
00248         switch (sock->struct_type) {
00249         case SOCK_STRUCT_NONE:
00250             switch (sock->type) {
00251             case SOCK_FLOAT:
00252                 NODE_DEFINE_SUBTYPES_FLOAT
00253                 break;
00254             case SOCK_INT:
00255                 NODE_DEFINE_SUBTYPES_INT
00256                 break;
00257             case SOCK_BOOLEAN:
00258                 return &RNA_NodeSocketBoolean;
00259             case SOCK_VECTOR:
00260                 NODE_DEFINE_SUBTYPES_VECTOR
00261                 break;
00262             case SOCK_RGBA:
00263                 return &RNA_NodeSocketRGBA;
00264             case SOCK_SHADER:
00265                 return &RNA_NodeSocketShader;
00266             }
00267             break;
00268         case SOCK_STRUCT_OUTPUT_FILE:
00269             return &RNA_NodeImageFileSocket;
00270         }
00271         
00272         #undef SUBTYPE
00273     }
00274     
00275     return &RNA_NodeSocket;
00276 }

00278 static char *rna_NodeSocket_path(PointerRNA *ptr)
00279 {
00280     bNodeTree *ntree = (bNodeTree*)ptr->id.data;
00281     bNodeSocket *sock = (bNodeSocket*)ptr->data;
00282     bNode *node;
00283     int socketindex;
00284     
00285     /* group sockets */
00286     socketindex = BLI_findindex(&ntree->inputs, sock);
00287     if (socketindex != -1)
00288         return BLI_sprintfN("inputs[%d]", socketindex);
00289     
00290     socketindex = BLI_findindex(&ntree->outputs, sock);
00291     if (socketindex != -1)
00292         return BLI_sprintfN("outputs[%d]", socketindex);
00293     
00294     /* node sockets */
00295     if (!nodeFindNode(ntree, sock, &node, NULL, NULL)) return NULL;
00296     
00297     socketindex = BLI_findindex(&node->inputs, sock);
00298     if (socketindex != -1)
00299         return BLI_sprintfN("nodes[\"%s\"].inputs[%d]", node->name, socketindex);
00300     
00301     socketindex = BLI_findindex(&node->outputs, sock);
00302     if (socketindex != -1)
00303         return BLI_sprintfN("nodes[\"%s\"].outputs[%d]", node->name, socketindex);
00304     
00305     return NULL;
00306 }

00688 static bNodeLink *rna_NodeTree_link_new(bNodeTree *ntree, ReportList *reports,
00689                                         bNodeSocket *fromsock, bNodeSocket *tosock)
00690 {
00691     bNodeLink *ret;
00692     bNode *fromnode = NULL, *tonode = NULL;
00693     int from_in_out, to_in_out;
00694 
00695     nodeFindNode(ntree, fromsock, &fromnode, NULL, &from_in_out);
00696     nodeFindNode(ntree, tosock, &tonode, NULL, &to_in_out);
00697     
00698     if (&from_in_out == &to_in_out) {
00699         BKE_reportf(reports, RPT_ERROR, "Same input/output direction of sockets");
00700         return NULL;
00701     }
00702 
00703     /* unlink node input socket */
00704     if (to_in_out == SOCK_IN)
00705         nodeRemSocketLinks(ntree, tosock);
00706     else
00707         nodeRemSocketLinks(ntree, fromsock);
00708 
00709     ret = nodeAddLink(ntree, fromnode, fromsock, tonode, tosock);
00710     
00711     if (ret) {
00712         nodeUpdate(ntree, tonode);
00713 
00714         ntreeUpdateTree(ntree);
00715 
00716         WM_main_add_notifier(NC_NODE|NA_EDITED, ntree);
00717     }
00718 
00719     return ret;
00720 }

03136 static void rna_def_node_socket_subtype(BlenderRNA *brna, int type, int subtype, const char *name, const char *ui_name)
03137 {

03143     static EnumPropertyItem subtype_items[] = {
03144         NODE_DEFINE_SUBTYPES
03145         {0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL}
03146     };
03147     #undef SUBTYPE
03148 
03149     #define SUBTYPE(socktype, stypename, id, idname)    if (subtype == (PROP_##id)) propsubtype = PROP_##id;
03150     NODE_DEFINE_SUBTYPES
03151     #undef SUBTYPE
03152     
03153     srna = RNA_def_struct(brna, name, "NodeSocket");
03154     RNA_def_struct_ui_text(srna, ui_name, "Input or output socket of a node");
03155     RNA_def_struct_sdna(srna, "bNodeSocket");
03156     RNA_def_struct_ui_icon(srna, ICON_PLUG);
03157     RNA_def_struct_path_func(srna, "rna_NodeSocket_path");
03158     
03159     switch (type) {
03160     case SOCK_INT:
03161         RNA_def_struct_sdna_from(srna, "bNodeSocketValueInt", "default_value");
03162         
03163         prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "subtype", PROP_ENUM, PROP_NONE);
03164         RNA_def_property_enum_sdna(prop, NULL, "subtype");
03165         RNA_def_property_enum_items(prop, subtype_items);
03166         RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Subtype", "Subtype defining the socket value details");
03167         RNA_def_property_update(prop, NC_NODE|NA_EDITED, "rna_NodeSocket_update");
03168         
03169         prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "default_value", PROP_INT, propsubtype);
03170         RNA_def_property_int_sdna(prop, NULL, "value");
03171         RNA_def_property_int_funcs(prop, NULL, NULL, "rna_NodeSocketInt_range");
03172         RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Default Value", "");
03173         RNA_def_property_update(prop, NC_NODE|NA_EDITED, "rna_NodeSocket_update");
03174         break;
03175     case SOCK_FLOAT:
03176         RNA_def_struct_sdna_from(srna, "bNodeSocketValueFloat", "default_value");
03177         
03178         prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "subtype", PROP_ENUM, PROP_NONE);
03179         RNA_def_property_enum_sdna(prop, NULL, "subtype");
03180         RNA_def_property_enum_items(prop, subtype_items);
03181         RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Subtype", "Subtype defining the socket value details");
03182         RNA_def_property_update(prop, NC_NODE|NA_EDITED, "rna_NodeSocket_update");
